00062 /*
00063  * Test retrieving a DataGroup configured to read data using memory-mapping
00064  */
00065 void GenericDataFileBasedTest::DataGroupMMTest()
00066 {
00067         GenericData data;
00068         GenericFileReader reader;
00069         reader.SetFilename(TEST_DATA_DAT_FILE);
00070         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.ReadHeader(data, GenericFileReader::ReadNoDataGroupHeader));
00071 
00072         u_int32_t addr = data.Header().GetFirstDataGroupFilePos();
00073         DataGroup dc = data.DataGroup(addr);
00074 
00075         // Check that we can get a DataSet and use it
00076         DataSet* dataPlane = dc.DataSet(0);
00077         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dataPlane);
00078 
00079         dataPlane->Open();
00080         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dataPlane->BytesPerRow() == 2);
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dataPlane->Rows() == 100);
00082         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dataPlane->Cols() == 1);
00083 
00084         int32_t rows = dataPlane->Rows();
00085         for( int32_t row = 0; row < rows; ++row )
00086         {
00087                 u_int16_t expected = (u_int16_t)(row*10+row);
00088                 u_int16_t value;
00089                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(dataPlane->GetData(row, 0, value));
00090                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(value == expected);
00091         }
00092 
00093         dataPlane->Close();     // optional - Delete will call this
00094         dataPlane->Delete();
00095 }
